code: @Bean public BasicBatchConfigurer batchConfigurer(BatchProperties properties, DataSource dataSource, ObjectProvider<TransactionManagerCustomizers> transactionManagerCustomizers) {     return new BasicBatchConfigurer(properties, dataSource, transactionManagerCustomizers.getIfAvailable()). }

@Bean public JpaBatchConfigurer batchConfigurer(BatchProperties properties, DataSource dataSource, ObjectProvider<TransactionManagerCustomizers> transactionManagerCustomizers, EntityManagerFactory entityManagerFactory) {     return new JpaBatchConfigurer(properties, dataSource, transactionManagerCustomizers.getIfAvailable(), entityManagerFactory). }
